<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Core, Masterclass 연수 신청</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/images/favicon.png">
    
    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <!-- AOS Library -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable.css" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --mdbf-blue: #3364D9;
            --mdbf-blue-hover: #1B4BBE;
            --mdbf-blue-weak: #F0F4FF;
            --mdbf-grey-50: #F9FAFB;
            --mdbf-grey-100: #F2F4F6;
            --mdbf-grey-200: #E5E8EB;
            --mdbf-grey-600: #6B7684;
            --mdbf-grey-800: #333D4B;
            --mdbf-radius-md: 12px;
            --mdbf-radius-lg: 20px;
            --apple-grey: #1D1D1F;
            --samsung-white: #F4F4F4;
        }
        body {
            font-family: "Pretendard Variable", -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: var(--mdbf-grey-800);
            word-break: keep-all;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--mdbf-blue);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            border-radius: var(--mdbf-radius-md);
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--mdbf-blue-hover);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(51, 100, 217, 0.2);
        }
        .toss-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid var(--mdbf-grey-100);
            border-radius: var(--mdbf-radius-lg);
            padding: 32px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .toss-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .nav-blur {
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }
        .timetable-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .tag-high { background-color: #E0F2FE; color: #0369A1; }
        .tag-normal { background-color: #FEF9C3; color: #854D0E; }
        
        .watermark-link {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 300;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94A3B8;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .watermark-link:hover { color: #ffffff; }

        #back-to-top {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: var(--mdbf-blue);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            cursor: pointer;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        #back-to-top.show { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; }
        #back-to-top:hover { background-color: var(--mdbf-blue-hover); transform: translateY(-3px); }

        .premium-text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D1D1F 0%, #3364D9 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .capsule-frame {
            border-radius: 999px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: var(--samsung-white);
            aspect-ratio: 1 / 1.35;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .instructor-img-placeholder {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #E5E7EB 0%, #9CA3AF 100%);
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: filter 0.5s ease;
        }
        .capsule-frame:hover .instructor-img-placeholder { filter: grayscale(0%); }
        .hero-title { letter-spacing: -0.05em; line-height: 1.05; font-weight: 900; }
        .btn-ios {
            background-color: var(--mdbf-blue);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 20px 60px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(51, 100, 217, 0.3);
        }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white">

    <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 nav-blur border-b border-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-[72px] flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center">
                <img src="assets/images/logo_nav.png" alt="MDBF Logo" class="h-10 md:h-12">
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-[15px] font-medium text-gray-600">
                <a href="#info" class="hover:text-black transition-colors">연수 정보</a>
                <a href="#curriculum-high" class="hover:text-black transition-colors">하이엔드 과정</a>
                <a href="#curriculum-normal" class="hover:text-black transition-colors">캐주얼 과정</a>
                <a href="#apply" class="hover:text-black transition-colors">신청하기</a>
            </div>
            <a href="#apply" class="bg-[#3364D9] text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-[10px] text-[14px] font-bold hover:bg-[#1B4BBE] transition-all">
                신청하기
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section id="intro" class="pt-[220px] pb-[120px] px-6">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-20">
            <div class="flex-1 text-left">
                <div data-aos="fade-right" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-[13px] font-black mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest">
                    2026 MDBF Open Training
                </div>
                <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="hero-title text-[50px] md:text-[90px] premium-text-gradient mb-10 leading-[1.05]">
                    The Core,<br/>Masterclass
                </h1>
                <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="text-[20px] md:text-[28px] text-gray-400 font-medium mb-12 leading-tight">
                    미래 교육의 핵심을 찌르는 단 하나의 마스터클래스.<br/>서울교대에서 전문가들의 실전 노하우를 경험하세요.
                </p>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                    <a href="list.html" class="btn-ios inline-block text-white">연수 신청하기</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 relative w-full" data-aos="fade-left">
                <div class="w-full aspect-square bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-600 to-indigo-400 rounded-[80px] rotate-6 opacity-10 absolute -top-10 -right-10"></div>
                <div class="w-full aspect-video md:aspect-square rounded-[40px] md:rounded-[60px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative z-10 bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-300 font-black text-[40px]">
                    CORE VISUAL
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="info" class="bg-[#F9FAFB] py-24 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0" class="toss-card">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-[#3364D9]">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-[22px] font-bold mb-3">연수 일정</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px]">5월 9일 (토)</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px]">12:00 — 17:30</p>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="toss-card">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-green-600">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path><path d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-[22px] font-bold mb-3">연수 장소</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px]">서울교육대학교</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px]">연구강의동</p>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="toss-card">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 text-purple-600">
                        <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-[22px] font-bold mb-3">신청 인원</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px]">각 강의별 최대 40명</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px]">선착순 정회원 우선 배정</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="curriculum-high" class="py-40 px-6 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-24">
                <span class="text-blue-600 font-black text-[18px] uppercase tracking-widest text-left block">Track 01</span>
                <h2 data-aos="fade-right" class="text-[40px] md:text-[64px] font-black tracking-tighter mt-4">High-end 연수 세션</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mb-16">
                <div data-aos="fade-up" class="space-y-6 group">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/이상선.png" alt="이상선" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-blue-600 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 1</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[24px] font-bold group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">바이브 코딩으로 시작하는 웹앱 개발 입문</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">이상선</p>
<p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-400 mt-1 leading-relaxed">그라운드 개발<br/>트라이디스 개발<br/>웹앱 개발 전문가</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="space-y-6 group">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/박창현.png" alt="박창현" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-blue-600 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 2</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[24px] font-bold group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">미드저니와 힉스필드로 완성하는 나만의 스튜디오</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">박창현</p>
<p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-400 mt-1 leading-relaxed">티처빌 온라인 직무연수 개발<br/>경기도 교육청 미디어 리터러시 영상 제작<br/>특성화고 생성형 AI 특강</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="space-y-6 group">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/임세범.png" alt="임세범" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-blue-600 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 3</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[24px] font-bold group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">AI한테 시켰는데 왜 내가 더 바쁘죠?— 클로드 코드 하네스로 답을 찾는 4시간</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">임세범</p>
<p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-400 mt-1 leading-relaxed">아이스크림 직무연수 개발<br/>GPT-API Chatbot 연구<br/>생성형 AI 활용 58제 저자</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div data-aos="fade-up" class="bg-blue-50/30 rounded-[24px] p-8 md:p-12 border border-blue-50">
                <h4 class="text-[20px] font-bold mb-8 text-blue-700">하이엔드 과정 공통 시간표</h4>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold w-36 shrink-0">13:00 - 14:50</span>
                        <div class="h-px bg-blue-200 grow"></div>
                        <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">1, 2교시 집중 세션</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold w-36 shrink-0">15:00 - 15:30</span>
                        <div class="h-px bg-orange-100 grow"></div>
                        <span class="text-gray-500 font-medium">네트워킹 및 휴식</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold w-36 shrink-0">15:30 - 17:20</span>
                        <div class="h-px bg-blue-200 grow"></div>
                        <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">3, 4교시 심화 세션</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="curriculum-normal" class="py-40 px-6 bg-[#F9FAFB]">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-24 text-right">
                <span class="text-amber-500 font-black text-[18px] uppercase tracking-widest block">Track 02</span>
                <h2 data-aos="fade-left" class="text-[40px] md:text-[64px] font-black tracking-tighter mt-4">Casual 연수 세션</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mb-16">
                <div data-aos="fade-up" class="space-y-6 group text-center">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/손수현.png" alt="손수현" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-amber-500 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 4</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">복잡한 교무 행정, 노션 하나로 스마트하게 관리하기</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">손수현</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="50" class="space-y-6 group text-center">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/황은지.png" alt="황은지" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-amber-500 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 5</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">2026 캔바 AI</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">황은지</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="space-y-6 group text-center">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/장성환.png" alt="장성환" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-amber-500 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 6</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">학교에서의 구글워크스페이스 활용법</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">장성환</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150" class="space-y-6 group text-center">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/채희재.png" alt="채희재" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-amber-500 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 7</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">교사를 위한 연수제작 설명서</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">채희재</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="space-y-6 group text-center">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/조민의.png" alt="조민의" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-amber-500 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 8</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">에듀테크 디톡스 - 교실 속 불필요한 디지털 덜어내기</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">조민의</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250" class="space-y-6 group text-center">
                    <div class="capsule-frame"><img src="assets/images/profile/박병우.png" alt="박병우" class="w-full h-full object-cover"></div>
                    <div class="px-2">
                        <span class="text-[12px] font-black text-amber-500 uppercase mb-2 block tracking-widest">강의실 9</span>
                        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">교실에서 바로 쓰는 창의 예술 움직임 놀이</h4>
                        <p class="text-lg font-bold text-mdbfBlue mt-2">박병우, 이정은</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div data-aos="fade-up" class="bg-gray-200/30 rounded-[24px] p-8 md:p-12 border border-gray-200">
                <h4 class="text-[20px] font-bold mb-8 text-gray-700">캐주얼 과정 공통 시간표</h4>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold w-36 shrink-0">13:00 - 13:50</span>
                        <div class="h-px bg-gray-300 grow"></div>
                        <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">1교시 본 세션</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold w-36 shrink-0">14:00 - 14:30</span>
                        <div class="h-px bg-orange-100 grow"></div>
                        <span class="text-gray-500 font-medium">네트워킹 및 휴식</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold w-36 shrink-0">14:30 - 15:20</span>
                        <div class="h-px bg-gray-300 grow"></div>
                        <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">2교시 본 세션</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="text-orange-500 font-bold w-36 shrink-0">15:30 - 16:00</span>
                        <div class="h-px bg-orange-100 grow"></div>
                        <span class="text-gray-500 font-medium">네트워킹 및 휴식 / 연수 종료</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="apply" class="py-28 px-6 text-center bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 data-aos="fade-up" class="text-[32px] md:text-[42px] font-bold mb-8">성장의 기회를 예약하세요</h2>
            <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="text-gray-500 mb-12 text-[18px] md:text-[20px]">몽당분필이 제안하는 핵심 전문과 과정 The Core, Masterclass</p>
                <div data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="200" class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                <a href="list.html" class="btn-primary px-20 py-5 text-[20px] shadow-xl w-full md:w-auto">
                    연수 신청하기
