        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-12 mb-16 pb-16 border-b border-white/10">
                <img src="assets/images/logo_white.png" alt="MDBF Logo White" class="h-14 w-auto object-contain">
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end gap-12">
                <div class="text-gray-400">
                    <p class="text-white font-bold mb-4 text-[16px]">@mdbf</p>
                    <div class="space-y-1.5 text-[14px] leading-relaxed">
                        <p>사업장소재지: 인천광역시 남동구 호구포로 183, 604호 (고잔동, 후이즈스마트타워)</p>
                        <p>법인등록번호: 120121-0023788 | 개업연월일: 2024년 01월 02일</p>
                        <p class="text-white font-semibold">010-3643-6790 | mdbftv@naver.com</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right flex flex-col items-end gap-6">
